                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Consul-General <persName type="from">Steinhart</persName> to
                        the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Habana</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1906-09-10">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 10, 1906</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>President here worried because no reply received my message, and asks war vessels
                    be sent immediately.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Steinhart</hi>,<lb/>
                        <hi rend="italic">Consul-General.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
